metadata.name: Outdoors
metadata.description:
"Outdoors" is a call to nature, a celebration of the calm that comes with the cool air, a crackling fire, and the unmistakable smell of burning wood and smoke that fills the air.

Format: MP4
Length: 10 Seconds, Sound (Looped)
Size: 2500x2500
Additions: High-Resolution static image included for print purposes.
